    "body": "I am able to reproduce the issue with a similar folder structure on Ubuntu 12.04. I'm using the latest versions of Sublime Text 2 and SublimeClang. I added both the source and header folder to the sublime-project file, but does not help.\n\nFor some cases it works though, as long as the implementation and the definition are on the same file,. However, that is hardly the case for typical h, cpp usage."
